The problem really was on mobile devices with a cache, the browser caches files and there was also a cache on the server side. On the server, I cleared, but in the browser I have to do it myself. If you are using Chrome, then you need to open the browser menu (3 vertical dots), go to the History menu and clear everything, the item with passwords can be left unchecked.
